      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十二月六日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2059.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 2.86
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3333332999996,
          "startTime": 3.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.3333333,
          "startTime": 8.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9899.999999999998,
          "startTime": 10.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "今日発売のkanaの写真集、売り上げも好調らしいし\nみんな感想呟いてくれてるかな～",
      "startTime": 8.1694163125,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8830.583689300001,
          "startTime": 17.0000000018
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11410.583687499999,
          "startTime": 19.58
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？　なんで？　kanaがトレンドにのってない！\n一位「♯赤崎こころ誕生祭」……？　マジでムカつく！",
      "startTime": 16.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6233.333905599999,
          "startTime": 23.2000005723
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざこころの誕生日に写真集出すなんて\nkanaちゃんはこころのことが大好きなんですね～！",
      "startTime": 26.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ？　被せたくて被せた訳じゃねーから！\n偶然！　被っただけだから！",
      "startTime": 33.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6500.0007646999975,
          "startTime": 40.1000007647
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "残念でしたね、残念でしたね、残念でしたねぇ？\nトレンド一位を独占中！　赤崎こころ愛されてまーす",
      "startTime": 40.0666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "このクソガキ……あれ？　角はどうしたの\nいつもと雰囲気違うじゃん",
      "startTime": 51.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまでリズノワのみんなにお誕生日を\nお祝いしてもらってたんですよ～！",
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、酔っぱらった莉央さんがどーしてもこころの髪\nを結いたいって言うから仕方なく……へ、変ですか？",
      "startTime": 62.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "悪くないんじゃない？　めっちゃ似合ってるよ\n莉央って、意外と手先器用なんだね～",
      "startTime": 72.838784816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。ま、まあ、こころは何でも似合うんですけど～\nこころの良さを引き出す莉央さんもさすがですよね～",
      "startTime": 80.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　聞いて下さいよ、kanaちゃん～！\nこころの先輩達、本当に可愛いんですよ～！",
      "startTime": 87.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "自分達が『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の\n生放送に呼ばれなかったのをすっごく根に持ってて！",
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんが「私は今日一日中こころと一緒にいたから\n沢山お祝いしました」ってマウント取り始めたら",
      "startTime": 102.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんは真面目な顔して「僕はカニカマと後輩に\n気を遣われるのが嫌いなんだ」って言ってくるし",
      "startTime": 110.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも「次変な気を遣ったら最高のヤキモチを\n味わわせてあげる」とかって……ぷっ、あははは～",
      "startTime": 119.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……あんた達、本当に仲いいよね～\n最高のヤキモチってなんだよそれ、美味しそうだけど",
      "startTime": 129.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "食べ物の「焼餅」ではないと思いますよ？\nこころが好き過ぎて嫉妬しちゃうって意味のヤキモ……",
      "startTime": 137.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "うぜー！　分かってるっつーの！\n解説しなくていいから！　てか、写真撮ろうよ！",
      "startTime": 142.9333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日かつ、いつもと違う髪型のあんたと撮った写真\nなんてバズるの確定だし！　ほら、近く寄って！",
      "startTime": 151.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "あー……ごめんなさい、撮るだけならいいんですけど\nこの写真はSNSに載せないでくれますか？",
      "startTime": 160.8333099364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "は？　なんで？\nせっかくバズ確なのにもったいないじゃん",
      "startTime": 166.8999949137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん沢山の人に見て欲しい気持ちもあるんですけど\nこころだけの宝物にしたい気持ちもあり……",
      "startTime": 174.5999949137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "その……せっかく莉央さんが四人だけのこころの\nお誕生日会のためにアレンジしてくれたので……",
      "startTime": 182.7666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……分かった。今日は写真撮るのやめとくわ\n莉央からヤキモチの流れ弾食らうのもごめんだし",
      "startTime": 192.1666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。ほんと、愛されてんな。こころは",
      "startTime": 195.8333010991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "はい～！　薄々「そうかな～」って思ってたのですが\n今日、十二月六日にそれが確信に変わりました！",
      "startTime": 204.4666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "愛され過ぎてこころが困っちゃうくらい愛ちゃんも\n葵さんも、莉央さんもこころのことが大好きなんです～",
      "startTime": 212.000004069,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}